http://www.thehindu.com/news/national/andhra-pradesh/Tortured-child-rescued-in-Prakasam/article13984410.ece

In a joint operation, Childline India Foundation NGO partner HELP and Prakasam police rrescued a 4-year-old boy, who was tortured by his adopted parents at Chinnaganjam in Prakasam District on Wednesday.The boy, Siva, was shifted to the rescue home at Machavaram, near here on the orders of Child Welfare Committee Chairman B.V.S.N.K. Prasad.